>
  <div style="padding: 2rem; max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h1>Documentation</h1>
    <p>
      Complete guides, API reference, and architecture documentation for
      FraiseQL.
    </p>

    <section style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <h2>Getting Started</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#install">Installation</a></li>
        <li><a href="#quickstart">Quick Start Guide</a></li>
        <li><a href="#first-api">Build Your First API</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <h2>Guides</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Schema Authoring</li>
        <li>Database Migrations with Confiture</li>
        <li>Deployment & Operations</li>
        <li>Security & Compliance</li>
        <li>Performance Optimization</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <h2>Reference</h2>
